com.nexmo.clientcore.network

Class NetworkManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nexmo.clientcore.network.NetworkManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRtcNetwork

    public class NetworkManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements IRtcNetwork
    Created by ibendayan on 20/03/2018. This class is a public API for a single network related request. It validates the given arguments, creates the relevant requests, and passes them to the relevant manager (socket or http).
